RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT contract_ref_no, user_ref_no, branch, desk_code, expense_code, portfolio, portfolio_desc, position_qualifier, position_identifier, cusip_no, ticket_id, currency, curvr, totvr FROM (SELECT a.contract_ref_no, a.user_ref_no, a.branch, b.desk_code, b.expense_code, b.portfolio, c.portfolio_desc, b.position_qualifier, b.position_identifier, b.cusip_no, b.ticket_id, b.currency, (select count(1) from tltb_fee_liqd_detail d where d.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) curvr , (select count(1) from tltb_fee_liqd_detail d where d.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) totvr FROM oltbs_contract a, tltbs_contract_master b, tltms_portfolio c WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND a.latest_version_no = b.version_no AND a.BRANCH = global.current_branch AND c.portfolio = b.portfolio AND a.module_code = 'TL' AND a.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO)
